caption.title: Comparison of the size of rJEVs-forming foci by micro-antigen focus assay utilizing VERO cells.
caption.p: (A) The focus was viewed by light microscopy. (B) The size of focus was estimated by ImageJ version 1.44. Mean with SEM for four foci is showed. The difference in size was calculated using one-way ANOVA followed by Turkeyâ€™s Multiple Comparison Test.
